inal in Action",[1528],{"type":149,"attrs":1529},{"color":18},"FeaturedResourceGrid",[1532,1533,1534],"e3d4d108-2e13-489f-87cb-66faa4087e3a","8158c4aa-2998-4ba4-a3f5-998987c00907","835d04db-73c8-46d2-bb1a-15f0c44b5ebf",{"_uid":1536,"headline":1537,"component":1530,"padding_top":18,"padding_bottom":18,"featured_resource":1556},"50b97a0d-0a91-4a03-94f0-f4a82fd6966b",{"type":66,"content":1538},[1539,1547],{"type":69,"attrs":1540,"content":1541},{"level":138,"textAlign":1516},[1542],{"text":1543,"type":75,"marks":1544},"Explore more ways to get started",[1545],{"type":149,"attrs":1546},{"color":18},{"type":112,"attrs":1548,"content":1549},{"textAlign":1516},[1550,1551],{"type":618},{"text":1552,"type":75,"marks":1553},"Choose the path that fits your timeline — learn, explore, or connect when you're ready.",[1554],{"type":149,"attrs":1555},{"color":1296},[1557,1558,1559],"9bcda1f6-f761-4503-9cfc-8d2968b2245d","3af37708-5188-42ed-ba8c-be3a08da1e4c","a4d2fe51-f388-42f8-8b3c-98dd610d3d22",{"_uid":1561,"headline":1562,"component":1580,"padding_top":1419,"show_all_link":1581,"padding_bottom":1419,"featured_resource":1582},"cc78035e-3af3-4081-8b5b-1402e48fe612",{"type":66,"content":1563},[1564,1572],{"type":112,"attrs":1565,"content":1566},{"textAlign":139},[1567],{"text":1568,"type":75,"marks":1569},"Competitive comparision",[1570],{"type":149,"attrs":1571},{"color":151},{"type":69,"attrs":1573,"content":1574},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[1575],{"text":1576,"type":75,"marks":1577},"Check out How Terminal Stacks up vs. the Competition",[1578],{"type":149,"attrs":1579},{"color":18},"FeaturedResourceSection",{"id":18,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":18},[1583,1584,1585,1586,1587,1588,1589,1590,1591,1592],"bed8a66b-30ed-4bc8-8e60-febde05e3d5f","f69407f4-8e32-4ebd-8062-9e2117040e8f","6c52152d-bc76-4a6c-9c4c-ed2ef39df895","e7a31d8e-47e8-4598-aea1-b507a313d86e","94d55377-e7fe-4bf6-9fc3-ffa8536463b7","aa006f36-8f12-493c-90ec-4294592d076c","5cf08e72-f671-450d-972d-88ca323846f8","2781a62c-9964-42bb-ab31-635256152390","cd5ec51d-9e26-4a05-8f85-55f0c0d5146f","f7921fd6-3eef-4dc8-bee9-81d11ee7e607",{"_uid":1594,"tabs":1595,"content":1935,"component":1947},"d1d003bd-db01-4d22-9c1b-da508f68deb3",[1596,1702,1784,1866],{"_uid":1597,"items":1598,"label":1700,"component":1701},"7eeb2631-a584-43b5-a7fe-1f801476952d",[1599,1636,1661,1674,1687],{"_uid":1600,"title":1601,"content":1602,"component":1635},"67c4c4ec-669a-46e9-b090-e1e4c2cfba73","What does Terminal actually do?",{"type":66,"content":1603},[1604],{"type":112,"attrs":1605,"content":1606},{"textAlign":139},[1607,1613,1620,1625,1630],{"text":1608,"type":75,"marks":1609},"Terminal is an AI-native Yard Operating System",[1610],{"type":149,"attrs":1611},{"color":1612},"#1F1F1F",{"text":1614,"type":75,"marks":1615},"TM",[1616,1618],{"type":149,"attrs":1617},{"color":1612},{"type":1619},"superscript",{"text":1621,"type":75,"marks":1622}," (YOS",[1623],{"type":149,"attrs":1624},{"color":1612},{"text":1614,"type":75,"marks":1626},[1627,1629],{"type":149,"attrs":1628},{"color":1612},{"type":1619},{"text":1631,"type":75,"marks":1632},") that uses computer vision to automate yard execution from gate to dock. It replaces manual logs with a system that proactively decides and executes the next best move in real-time.",[1633],{"type":149,"attrs":1634},{"color":1612},"TabbedAccordionItem",{"_uid":1637,"title":1638,"content":1639,"component":1635},"a9365770-e975-4ce2-b104-8d0217853953","How is this different from a traditional Yard Management System (YMS)?",{"type":66,"content":1640},[1641],{"type":112,"attrs":1642,"content":1643},{"textAlign":139},[1644,1649,1656],{"text":1645,"type":75,"marks":1646},"Traditional YMS are \"digital clipboards\" that record what already happened; Terminal is an ",[1647],{"type":149,"attrs":1648},{"color":1612},{"text":1650,"type":75,"marks":1651},"operating",[1652,1654],{"type":149,"attrs":1653},{"color":1612},{"type":1655},"italic",{"text":1657,"type":75,"marks":1658}," system that sees what is happening now and orchestrates what needs to happen next in the yard. ",[1659],{"type":149,"attrs":1660},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1662,"title":1663,"content":1664,"component":1635},"6057177b-869b-4ddd-a6a5-f6f9e1667d56","What is \"Agentic AI\" in the context of the yard?",{"type":66,"content":1665},[1666],{"type":112,"attrs":1667,"content":1668},{"textAlign":139},[1669],{"text":1670,"type":75,"marks":1671},"It acts as a 24/7 autonomous supervisor that handles exceptions and reprioritizes tasks based on real-time conditions, ensuring the most critical moves happen first (e.g. how to prepare and reallocate resources for a late appointment)",[1672],{"type":149,"attrs":1673},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1675,"title":1676,"content":1677,"component":1635},"13d194f8-3ac3-415e-8231-389b0824c9fc","How accurate is the data captured by your system?",{"type":66,"content":1678},[1679],{"type":112,"attrs":1680,"content":1681},{"textAlign":139},[1682],{"text":1683,"type":75,"marks":1684},"Our proprietary computer vision stack delivers 50%or more improvement in data accuracy vs. manual operations, virtually eliminating the human error and \"lost assets\" common with manual entry.",[1685],{"type":149,"attrs":1686},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1688,"title":1689,"content":1690,"component":1635},"3b9220e6-02d1-4f72-bc81-356f80bdc4a3","Can we manage multiple sites from a single login?",{"type":66,"content":1691},[1692],{"type":112,"attrs":1693,"content":1694},{"textAlign":139},[1695],{"text":1696,"type":75,"marks":1697},"Yes; Terminal provides a \"Global Control Tower\" view, allowing you to compare KPIs, dwell times, and performance across all facilities in your network in one place.",[1698],{"type":149,"attrs":1699},{"color":1612},"Core Technology","TabbedAccordionTab",{"_uid":1703,"items":1704,"label":1783,"component":1701},"ed98d17c-3e6c-4494-91b6-08b47b1e8af8",[1705,1718,1731,1744,1757,1770],{"_uid":1706,"title":1707,"content":1708,"component":1635},"b07e6958-dca2-474b-a95f-d6a93b5f7e2b","How is Terminal priced?",{"type":66,"content":1709},[1710],{"type":112,"attrs":1711,"content":1712},{"textAlign":139},[1713],{"text":1714,"type":75,"marks":1715},"Terminal is priced as a competitive annual, all-inclusive as-a-service model for all hardware, support, and services. Deployments can vary and are charged as a separate up-front fee.",[1716],{"type":149,"attrs":1717},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1719,"title":1720,"content":1721,"component":1635},"220afd0f-7d8f-433c-a008-7dbf57a1bbd1","What kind of ROI can I expect?",{"type":66,"content":1722},[1723],{"type":112,"attrs":1724,"content":1725},{"textAlign":139},[1726],{"text":1727,"type":75,"marks":1728},"Most customers see a 4x+ ROI within the first year and achieve a full payback in less than 5 months through labor savings and faster throughput.",[1729],{"type":149,"attrs":1730},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1732,"title":1733,"content":1734,"component":1635},"d1dc8ead-7f4c-4b55-b674-c7bf1d5d30a1","How does Terminal reduce carrier and facility costs?",{"type":66,"content":1735},[1736],{"type":112,"attrs":1737,"content":1738},{"textAlign":139},[1739],{"text":1740,"type":75,"marks":1741},"We reduce driver detention fees by improving gate processing times, faster responsiveness at the dock, and maximum visibility to all asset inventory in the yard. ",[1742],{"type":149,"attrs":1743},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1745,"title":1746,"content":1747,"component":1635},"1f81a979-6291-4697-b775-082984e71b1c","Can Terminal help with regulatory compliance?",{"type":66,"content":1748},[1749],{"type":112,"attrs":1750,"content":1751},{"textAlign":139},[1752],{"text":1753,"type":75,"marks":1754},"Yes; our Indirect Source Rule (ISR) feature automates compliance by generating audit-ready data for regulations like Rule 2305.",[1755],{"type":149,"attrs":1756},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1758,"title":1759,"content":1760,"component":1635},"8af4e52d-6959-44f1-ac5d-330c56c84414","Who is Terminal best suited for?",{"type":66,"content":1761},[1762],{"type":112,"attrs":1763,"content":1764},{"textAlign":139},[1765],{"text":1766,"type":75,"marks":1767},"Terminal is built for enterprise 3PLs, retailers, and manufacturers managing complex, medium- to high-volume mutli-yard networks that want to scale without adding headcount.",[1768],{"type":149,"attrs":1769},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1771,"title":1772,"content":1773,"component":1635},"82762bbd-c9cb-41d8-9e18-9d1ad13a998a","Is Terminal a stable long-term partner? ",{"type":66,"content":1774},[1775],{"type":112,"attrs":1776,"content":1777},{"textAlign":139},[1778],{"text":1779,"type":75,"marks":1780},"Founded in 2023 and backed by 8VC and four of the top 10 U.S. logistics firms (including Prologis and Ryder), Terminal offers deep financial and strategic stability.",[1781],{"type":149,"attrs":1782},{"color":1612},"Value",{"_uid":1785,"items":1786,"label":1865,"component":1701},"fe108c93-b615-46ad-8004-0a0e774a6298",[1787,1800,1813,1826,1839,1852],{"_uid":1788,"title":1789,"content":1790,"component":1635},"2e4b4e5d-a4f9-4904-b472-00d357ffe812","How fast can we go live?",{"type":66,"content":1791},[1792],{"type":112,"attrs":1793,"content":1794},{"textAlign":139},[1795],{"text":1796,"type":75,"marks":1797},"Gate automation can be live in as little as 5 days, with full yard orchestration typically completed in 45 days.",[1798],{"type":149,"attrs":1799},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1801,"title":1802,"content":1803,"component":1635},"60d4de18-7cf6-4c49-9059-413071d39a51","Does Terminal integrate with my existing WMS/TMS?",{"type":66,"content":1804},[1805],{"type":112,"attrs":1806,"content":1807},{"textAlign":139},[1808],{"text":1809,"type":75,"marks":1810},"Yes; we offer seamless, event-driven integration with major platforms like Manhattan, SAP, Blue Yonder, FourKites, and project44.",[1811],{"type":149,"attrs":1812},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1814,"title":1815,"content":1816,"component":1635},"c5702309-fea8-42e2-bf85-ee50f6e40f12","Do I need to buy expensive proprietary cameras?",{"type":66,"content":1817},[1818],{"type":112,"attrs":1819,"content":1820},{"textAlign":139},[1821],{"text":1822,"type":75,"marks":1823},"No; Terminal is hardware-agnostic and can often leverage your existing IP cameras, or you can use our plug-and-play \"Terminal in a Camera\" bundles.",[1824],{"type":149,"attrs":1825},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1827,"title":1828,"content":1829,"component":1635},"5a37ebce-5484-4c61-a032-a83d88acfb9e","Is the platform modular or \"all-or-nothing\"?",{"type":66,"content":1830},[1831],{"type":112,"attrs":1832,"content":1833},{"textAlign":139},[1834],{"text":1835,"type":75,"marks":1836},"The system is highly configurable; you can start with a single use case, like Gate Acceleration, and expand into full yard orchestration over time.",[1837],{"type":149,"attrs":1838},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1840,"title":1841,"content":1842,"component":1635},"9bddd67f-1af3-464f-849e-87922d0941dd","What happens if our site’s internet goes down?",{"type":66,"content":1843},[1844],{"type":112,"attrs":1845,"content":1846},{"textAlign":139},[1847],{"text":1848,"type":75,"marks":1849},"Terminal is designed with local resilience; mission-critical tasks continue to buffer locally and sync to the cloud once connectivity is restored.",[1850],{"type":149,"attrs":1851},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1853,"title":1854,"content":1855,"component":1635},"445bf071-f02c-4210-85b2-5bbe5664357e","How does Terminal protect my data?",{"type":66,"content":1856},[1857],{"type":112,"attrs":1858,"content":1859},{"textAlign":139},[1860],{"text":1861,"type":75,"marks":1862},"We use a zero-trust security model with industry-standard encryption and are currently in the process of achieving SOC-2 compliance.",[1863],{"type":149,"attrs":1864},{"color":1612},"Implementation",{"_uid":1867,"items":1868,"label":1934,"component":1701},"ab585679-9d7b-49e0-a29f-9d46180c65ca",[1869,1882,1895,1908,1921],{"_uid":1870,"title":1871,"content":1872,"component":1635},"1dd20b08-4a33-4c1a-ab86-c8db2c612461","How do drivers and yard spotters interact with the system?",{"type":66,"content":1873},[1874],{"type":112,"attrs":1875,"content":1876},{"textAlign":139},[1877],{"text":1878,"type":75,"marks":1879},"Terminal is browser- based (not app to download!). Drivers can use their personal mobile devices, while spotters and dock workers can be outfitted with any browser-enabled mobile device approved by the operator. ",[1880],{"type":149,"attrs":1881},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1883,"title":1884,"content":1885,"component":1635},"71ed6e73-abc2-4b61-a9f8-ba7240b821bf","How does this change the role of my yard office staff?",{"type":66,"content":1886},[1887],{"type":112,"attrs":1888,"content":1889},{"textAlign":139},[1890],{"text":1891,"type":75,"marks":1892},"Staff shift from manual data entry to \"exception management,\" only intervening when the AI flags a specific issue that requires human judgment.",[1893],{"type":149,"attrs":1894},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1896,"title":1897,"content":1898,"component":1635},"729dea71-3358-47ab-908c-55826a84d904","Will implementation disrupt my current operations?",{"type":66,"content":1899},[1900],{"type":112,"attrs":1901,"content":1902},{"textAlign":139},[1903],{"text":1904,"type":75,"marks":1905},"No; our deployment model requires little operational downtime and carries a very low IT lift for your team.",[1906],{"type":149,"attrs":1907},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1909,"title":1910,"content":1911,"component":1635},"1dffc59c-2bfd-4e86-932d-7a5707d78359","What kind of support and training do you provide?",{"type":66,"content":1912},[1913],{"type":112,"attrs":1914,"content":1915},{"textAlign":139},[1916],{"text":1917,"type":75,"marks":1918},"We provide \"White-Glove\" on-site training for all shifts, 24/7 live technical support, and a dedicated hypercare period post-launch.",[1919],{"type":149,"attrs":1920},{"color":1612},{"_uid":1922,"title":1923,"content":1924,"component":1635},"5601cefa-5b18-475e-b7da-7ed4e655dbda","What is your system availability guarantee?",{"type":66,"content":1925},[1926],{"type":112,"attrs":1927,"content":1928},{"textAlign":139},[1929],{"text":1930,"type":75,"marks":1931},"As long as yard internet is running, Terminal runs at a 99.9% uptime for all mission-critical workflows to ensure your yard operations never stop.",[1932],{"type":149,"attrs":1933},{"color":1612},"Site Operations",{"type":66,"content":1936},[1937,1942],{"type":69,"attrs":1938,"content":1939},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[1940],{"text":1941,"type":75},"FAQs",{"type":112,"attrs":1943,"content":1944},{"textAlign":139},[1945],{"text":1946,"type":75},"Here are the most common questions teams have before getting started with Terminal.","TabbedAccordion",{"cta":1949,"_uid":1957,"body":1958,"logo":1959,"headline":1963,"component":1964},[1950],{"_uid":1951,"link":1952,"label":1955,"style":1956,"component":28},"34f5492c-b418-4783-aacc-714aa791b5cd",{"id":1953,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":1954},"b245fcac-d0f3-4e56-9fbe-f6c46f04191e","all-resources/terminal-yos-receives-second-5-star-gartner-peer-insights-review-terminal-delivers-immediate-efficiency-gains-and-consistent-long-term-platform-value-","SEE REVIEW","primary","121c272d-90c0-477a-a050-3d66494f06b5","Our overall experience with Terminal has been excellent. The solution is intuitive, dependable,\nand well-suited to complex, real world use ...",{"id":1960,"alt":18,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":1961,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":1962,"is_external_url":49},172878811170088,"/storyblok/f/337048/247x86/dbfb5813c8/gartner-peer-insights.svg",{},"“Terminal Delivers Immediate Efficiency Gains and Consistent Long-Term Platform Value”","Testimonial","StoryblokPage",{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":1967},{},"Contact - Terminal Industries",-40,[],"cb10c209-6ab7-4467-acf1-5dda87f30dfa","2025-05-09T13:05:35.576Z",[],[1975],{"name":1